{"tid":1669333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突破盲點]加泰同香港既性質係兩回事, 唔好問點解撐加泰而唔撐香港","createTime":"2019-10-22T13:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T01:46:21.000Z","uid":12149,"like":80,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb92959968cd42d5203253a82a792baad10107e","tid":1669333,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">加泰</span></span>本身已經係一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">民主制度下既自治區</span></span>, 本身擁有極大既自由度，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔需要爭取自由</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n其次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">加泰依家要既係獨立</span></strong></span>，並唔係好似香港咁爭取緊民主自由同五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，講返香港。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港一直以黎既訴求係講五大訴求，普選同人權</span></span></strong>，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">並唔係獨立</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國以至西方所支持既係香港爭取<span style=\"color: gold;\">民主自由</span>而並<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係獨立</span>，</span></span>唔該搞清楚。<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好踩落個陷阱度</span>講點解唔撐加泰，而撐香港，兩件事係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔同性質！</span></span><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"75d3399303409f03694cfe4d805806ef5b89c222","tid":1669333,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"8b722ef950946828a76b38cdd88d920700ff605c","tid":1669333,"uid":322508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco